  "description": "Zombies have a small chance of spawning with a shield, and they can use it to block attacks and projectiles.",
  "body": "<div align=\"center\">\n<h1>Shielded Zombies</h1>\n<a href=\"https://fabricmc.net\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Mod%20Loader-Fabric-lightyellow?logo=data:image/png;base64,\"></a>\n<img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Enviroment-Server-purple\">\n</div>\n\n\n<hr/>\n<div align=\"center\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/SG4gqJw2/images/3f8532ad73314e255854be439cdd34ae838ce49e.png\" alt=\"Main Image\"\n/>\n</div>\n<hr/>\n<br />\n\n### Description\nThis mod adds a small chance for zombies to spawn with a shield in their offhand.\n<br/>Shielded zombies can block melee attacks and projectiles, making combat more challenging and strategic.\n<br/>Perfect for players looking to add an extra layer of difficulty to their Minecraft experience.\n<br/>Can you survive the rise of the Shielded Zombies?\n\n\n### Modpack Permission:<br/>\nFeel free to use it in any modpacks.\n\n### Bug Report:<br/>\nReport bugs at the github page.\n\n\n",
